☕ Coffee Website

🌟 Overview

This is a Coffee Shop Website designed to showcase coffee products, menu, and store locations. The website provides an elegant and responsive user experience with modern web technologies.

🔹 Features

Home Page: Welcomes visitors with a stunning coffee-themed design.

About Section: Tells the story behind the coffee shop.

Menu Page: Displays coffee varieties with descriptions and prices.

Contact Page: Allows customers to get in touch.

Responsive Design: Works seamlessly on desktops, tablets, and mobile devices.

🛠️ Technologies Used

HTML - Structure of the website

CSS - Styling and layout

JavaScript - Interactivity and animations

Bootstrap (Optional) - For responsive design


Open the index.html file in your browser.

🎨 Customization

Modify styles.css to change colors, fonts, and layouts.

Update index.html with your own content and branding.

Enhance interactivity using script.js.
